Description: System service for checking APT package and firmware updates
 A system service that checks for available APT package updates and firmware
 updates, then sends desktop notifications.
 .
 The application runs two main checks:
  - APT package updates through apt update and cache inspection
  - Firmware updates through fwupdmgr
 .
 Notifications are sent using the freedesktop notification system. The package
 includes systemd timers for automated checking and maintenance tasks.